data.description: Introducing the epitome of modern comfort and style with this 3 bd, 3 ba nestled on a generously-sized corner lot, this sprawling ranch is a vision of perfection. From the moment you set foot onto the cedar-covered stoop, you'll be captivated by the craftsmanship that went into remodeling this residence. Step inside to discover the remarkable features. The kitchen adorned with stunning granite counters & a convenient butler's pantry is sure to inspire your culinary adventures. Indulge in luxury in the master suite, boasting a majestic marble shower & flooring, creating a spa-like oasis right at home. As you wander outside, a spacious patio beckons you to relax and entertain in style.NEW ROOF
